Date: Mon, 08 Jun 2026 18:35:00 +0000
Subject: [Z2-ASSESS-01] async job pattern for /assess endpoint

Replace synchronous blocking handler with async job pattern.
POST /assess returns immediately with job_id; GET /assess/{job_id} polls.

Root cause: 65s protocol sleep + LLM inference (~90-125s total) exceeds
Cloudflare proxy timeout, causing 502 on every call.

- Add in-memory _JOBS dict (per-container, benign on restart)
- Add _run_in_background() thread worker
- POST /assess: validate synchronously, spawn thread, return job_id
- GET /assess/{job_id}: poll endpoint
- No change to elicitation_service.py or wait_seconds semantics
- two_stage_verified purity contract preserved

Z2-ASSESS-01 ratified S-060826-03 · Charter Day 84
IC-035 closed: assess endpoint architecture now documented
